"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922078","Ministry of Defence","false","2018-06-14","<p>As part of the Modernising Defence Programme (MDP), we are considering options to ensure the UK has an AWACS capability beyond 2035. Further details will not be available until the full conclusion of the MDP.</p>","Aberconwy","Guto Bebb",,"2018-06-14T15:02:38.39Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922078/answer","Biography information for Guto Bebb","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922078/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/922078/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2018-06-11","AWACS","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what the UK’s sustainment strategy is for the UK AWACS capability beyond 2035.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","152071"
